Regional German dialect slang can be hugely different from one area to another, and Berliner Schnauze has its own special charm.&nbsp;
Because so many people new to Germany live in Berlin, it’s one of the dialects newcomers encounter the most, and it can be a bit confusing after learning High German, or Hochdeutsch, in a classroom setting.&nbsp;
Here are a few Berliner slang words that you can drop into your conversations to come off a bit more Berlinerisch.

